content:
GN128 Solutions an IT Solutions firm dedicated to helping clients leverage Information Technology to Increase profitability & efficiency.

We are recruiting to fill the position below:

Job Position: Junior Web Developer

Job Location: Ikeja, Lagos

Role Description





     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});






	We are currently looking to recruit a Junior Web Developer that is result oriented and self-motivated. You will be required to work from our office in Ikeja.
	This is a full-time on-site role for a Junior Web Developer with both front-end and back-end skills to work from our offices in Ikeja. The post holder will be undergo a two month Intensive training program to get up to speed working with the development team to develop both front-end and back-end functionalities of our tech products and supporting our applications.


Core Responsibilities and Duties


	Convert designs into HTML/PHP pages;
	Develop web sites in LARAVEL;
	Designing and creating databases for web pages;
	Convert designs into HTML/PHP pages;
	Connecting HTML/PHP pages to MYSQL Databases;
	Deploying websites into production
	CPanel Administration
	SSL Implementation & Website Security
	Optimizing developed features for maximum speed and scalability;
	Writing clean, readable, and testable code;
	Update and Fix existing issues with web pages
	Meet team deadlines;


Job Requirements


	Excellent Understanding web development life cycle;
	Experience with UI/UX Design;
	Excellent knowledge of REACT, HTML, CSS, Java and web development tools;
	Core working knowledge of PHP and LARAVEL;
	Database Design & Development, MYSQL/MSSQL;
	Search Engine Optimization;
	Ability to learn new concepts quickly.
	Flexible approach, self-motivated and organised;


Person Specification:


	Good interpersonal skills, able to communicate in a friendly, open and constructive manner;
	Able to work on own initiative with minimal supervision;
	Ability to work as a team player with the team;
	Ability to learn & understand new concepts quickly;
	Ability to pay attention to details & produce work of a high standard;
	Flexible approach, self-motivated and organised


Experience:


	Minimum of 12 months professional experience
	Flexible work approach, self-motivated and organised.


Salary
N150,000.00 / month.

Method of Application
Interested and qualified candidates should send their CV to: recruit@gn128.com using the Job Position as the subject of the email.

Note: Only candidates that live in Lagos and within 30mins commuting of Ikeja would be considered.    



        Click here to Apply  









